<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf010c47d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7510"><num value="7510">§ 7510.</num><heading> Commodities not income</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Notwithstanding any other provision of law, commodities distributed under this chapter shall not be considered income or resources for any purposes under any Federal, State, or local law.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf010c47e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/8/tII/s206">Pub. L. 98–8, title II, § 206</ref>, <date date="1983-03-24">Mar. 24, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/36">97 Stat. 36</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
